title: Presence of drugs or metabolic products; admissibility
context: [ยง291E-22] Presence of drugs or metabolic products; admissibility. Any results reflecting the presence of drugs or metabolic products obtained from a blood or urine specimen obtained under this part shall not be admissible in any proceeding brought under chapter 329 or 712.
